OL,3,CFrost found on volcanoes near Mars'
OL,4,Cequator for first time
OL,6,FIt was first seen by the European
OL,7,FSpace Agency's (Esa) ExoMars Trace Gas
OL,8,FOrbiter (TGO), and later by both
OL,9,Fanother instruments aboard TGO and
OL,10,FEsa's Mars Express.
OL,12,FLead author Adomas Valantinas made the
OL,13,Fdiscovery as a PhD student at
OL,14,FUniversity of Bern, Switzerland, and
OL,15,Fis now a postdoctoral researcher at
OL,16,FBrown University, USA.
