OL,6,FEsa suggests that the amount of frost
OL,7,Frepresents about 150,000 tonnes of
OL,8,Fwater swapping between surface and
OL,9,Fatmosphere each day during the cold
OL,10,Fseasons, the equivalent of roughly 60
OL,11,FOlympic swimming pools.
OL,13,FThere are a number of possible for why
OL,14,Fthe frost had not been spotted until
OL,15,Fnow.
