OL,6,FThese include the orbit needing to
OL,7,Fline up in the right position in order
OL,8,Ffor the area to be observed in the
OL,9,Fearly morning, and another is needing
OL,10,Fto know where and when to look for the
OL,11,Ffrost.
OL,13,FDr Minjae Kim, research fellow,
OL,14,FDepartment of Physics, University of
OL,15,FWarwick, said the ice deposits must
OL,16,Fhave formed during Mars's ancient past
OL,17,Fwhen climatic conditions were "starkly
OL,18,Fdifferent".
